TV PERSONALITY Ntando Duma is one actress who is seemingly succeeding in the entertaining industry. After buying a Mercedes-Benz A200 AMG last November, she surprised many people when she shared a snap of her dream home on Friday. Ntando revealed last year that she had been building the house for her daughter, Sbahle. “I’ve been building my house since February last year and I’m so glad it is finally done. There’s no one who’s as ecstatic as Sbahle right now. Kunini yalinda ingane yami,” she said. ALSO READ | KENNETH NKOSI TALKS DIVORCE She posted a photo standing next to the swimming pool and pointing at the double-storey home, with the caption: “Ikhaya lomntanami (my baby’s home).” Congratulatory messages from fellow celebrities quickly started flooding in. Actor Clement Maosa said: “Don’t tell me about Ntando. She’s a hard worker that one; too focused. I call her comrade Winnie.” Then Ayanda Thabethe said: “This is a God dream. This is everything.” Others who congratulated her included rappers Cassper Nyovest and Boity Thulo.